{"type": "article", "id": 17837, "title": "“offset”木椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-20T07:10:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122431HaVemhwynpo0NqLX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款名为“offset”的木椅来自日本的设计工作室 Drill design，原本应该连接在一起的靠背和座位相互交叉，上下构成两个圆环。藤编座椅和靠背用了不同的颜色区分，使高脚凳似的座椅更明显，是很特别的结构。椅子可以两个重叠起来，它有两种靠背，一种是西式的环形靠背，一种是仿明式。<a href=\"http://www.drill-design.com/work-furniture/offset\" target=\"_blank\">这里是设计师的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122428uFrmEC8gd5xSTkRa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122429F3GctqZwLYevjVdl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122430c5CFQ9z7oIySriqT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122430OIBza79RYmhTdqFt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}